      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just social media though. it's like they've leaked stuff and now people at school are looking at me different too. i feel like i'm trapped in this loop where no matter what i do, it just gets worse. i feel like there's no actual way out of this. like there is no \"break\" that actually fixes how much everyone hates me. it just feels permanent.",
