    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. people tell me to talk to someone or just \"ignore it\" but that's not how it works. the pain is just always there. i look at the future and i literally see nothing but more of this. i just want to find a way to finally be at peace, you know? like a way to just not have to deal with the existence of all this anymore.",
